{"tid":352761,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一件(做/自己女朋友)最難頂既野","createTime":"2017-08-09T04:30:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-09T07:17:19.000Z","uid":131344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2c07753bc48bd46002371ade572f9cf8736d09c7","tid":352761,"uid":131344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T04:30:29.000Z","msg":"好鍾意瞓太鐘意瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日講講下嘢我都會瞓<br />\n男朋友之前都係講下笑  但係而家開始無奈咁望住我<br />\n我每晚都夠瞓 但我就係好想瞓 自己都控制唔到<br />\n男朋友成日都覺得我唔係好想聽佢講嘢所以瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申自我滿足 覺得自己各方面都唔錯"},{"pid":"96070ae2bd72f7b9cc6f8893d7f38c2d843ac0ba","tid":352761,"uid":13207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T04:32:19.000Z","msg":"渴睡症"},{"pid":"4ea136103471b7ee0d11b52c10852899f5da8689","tid":352761,"uid":131344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T04:36:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>渴睡症</blockquote><br />\n我都覺得我有  有冇咩症狀可以知有冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"601da6874760755392c45f64ac7df67381cb4dad","tid":352761,"uid":131344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T05:32:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1d8b428e8da8ae9b82bcf9ddbd30a7be8f51b497","tid":352761,"uid":17633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T07:08:12.000Z","msg":"睇醫生啦 咁誇張"},{"pid":"2236db04a895da1cda66dc929829dba797117e4b","tid":352761,"uid":132666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T07:17:19.000Z","msg":"我都一樣喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以傾計個陣盡量唔好係床<br />\n試過好多次傾傾下計啲睡意黎 <br />\n佢就話我會講：我唔得啦 好似就訓著啦<br />\n然後一秒訓著左好似大雄咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}